  {
    "row": 5,
    "rowsha": "5PaHTtIHjgCbFFsSxkLdsrfOcEv54zHdoZmUloMnreA=",
    "originContent": "[QuickLook](https://github.com/QL-Win/QuickLook) plugin for previewing various file types with [WebViewPlus](https://github.com/mooflu/WebViewPlus).",
    "translatedContent": "[QuickLook](https://github.com/QL-Win/QuickLook) 플러그인으로 [WebViewPlus](https://github.com/mooflu/WebViewPlus)를 사용하여 다양한 파일 형식을 미리 볼 수 있습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 6,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "RqdmG3NH9QjhcBwVYoBq8HuR78W7bVncMGUmjV1ox+w=",
    "originContent": "## Try out",
    "translatedContent": "## 사용해보기"
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "m+9478vw3lPC4bhKq/E+/DfmriVKzIRFARWKBCEa/aQ=",
    "originContent": "1. Go to [Release page](https://github.com/mooflu/QuickLook.Plugin.WebViewPlus/releases) and download the latest version.",
    "translatedContent": "1. [릴리스 페이지](https://github.com/mooflu/QuickLook.Plugin.WebViewPlus/releases)로 이동하여 최신 버전을 다운로드하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "czhiIn28NlyQ5HJYTrg0jFRUcADPxmwBii3VnGrbHjM=",
    "originContent": "2. Make sure that you have QuickLook running in the background. Go to your Download folder, and press <key>Spacebar</key> on the downloaded `.qlplugin` file.",
    "translatedContent": "2. QuickLook이 백그라운드에서 실행 중인지 확인하세요. 다운로드 폴더로 가서 다운로드한 `.qlplugin` 파일에서 <key>Spacebar</key> 키를 누르세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "XgqtwTOUUaGVRL5oV5p9DhViW7u+BVUrDomgRxrfOP4=",
    "originContent": "3. Click the “Install” button in the popup window.",
    "translatedContent": "3. 팝업 창에서 “설치” 버튼을 클릭하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "prL29LMwnQzXwkJRstfre2U1ElrLbnnGxKu60hdjX54=",
    "originContent": "4. Restart QuickLook.",
    "translatedContent": "4. QuickLook을 재시작하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "wjdFnWWOWVqIA3yQEwHKtlYZiAZgUsqUF4RWyr1jz/k=",
    "originContent": "5. To configure which file types to preview via WebViewPlus, open an html file and click the gears button on the bottom right.",
    "translatedContent": "5. WebViewPlus를 통해 미리 볼 파일 유형을 구성하려면, html 파일을 열고 오른쪽 아래의 톱니바퀴 버튼을 클릭하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "CLSMPQsYmPJH1xU0AtLw67b6Gv/bSXYVNK4RD/B1r9M=",
    "originContent": "## Development",
    "translatedContent": "## 개발"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "N6O+AdqUQVyevy+XQXnxVVPyNA5fC4J9YcFZGxlnuRA=",
    "originContent": " 1. Clone this project. Do not forget to update submodules.",
    "translatedContent": " 1. 이 프로젝트를 클론하세요. 서브모듈 업데이트를 잊지 마세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "Pfm5rnApsGOoFItCtF6e0siBbdnvOU7/PnUAlD4Wzao=",
    "originContent": " 2. Copy WebViewPlus web app to `webApp` or set plugin config `WebAppUrl` - see `WebpagePanel.cs`",
    "translatedContent": " 2. WebViewPlus 웹 앱을 `webApp`으로 복사하거나 플러그인 설정 `WebAppUrl`을 설정하세요 - `WebpagePanel.cs` 참조"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "fSgU2o/dXjT7ivCualRJfKxC1N62/x0DZ1l1fph0NHU=",
    "originContent": " 3. Set `Output path` in `Debug` configuration to something like `..\\QuickLook.upstream\\Build\\Debug\\QuickLook.Plugin\\QuickLook.Plugin.WebViewPlus\\`",
    "translatedContent": " 3. `Debug` 구성에서 `Output path`를 `..\\QuickLook.upstream\\Build\\Debug\\QuickLook.Plugin\\QuickLook.Plugin.WebViewPlus\\` 같은 경로로 설정하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "LVnLlm/dsxS9XUPLyw4ARVO7qnY5/a5H/s3zmIvoWpY=",
    "originContent": " 4. Build plugin project with `Debug` profile",
    "translatedContent": " 4. `Debug` 프로필로 플러그인 프로젝트를 빌드하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "9ANb2PbLBRyKn/eH4n/cVxkYI7o/E6YW62KPV4EpVJ0=",
    "originContent": " 5. Build and run upstream Quicklook with `Debug` profile",
    "translatedContent": " 5. `Debug` 프로필로 상위 QuickLook을 빌드하고 실행하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "GDbgX75b6AZXYavXOvzJ9mmgvywdDbjsT8VUUqv5QAs=",
    "originContent": " # Release",
    "translatedContent": " # 릴리스"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "6um5zGaIKOF9dZWoltaZRm9NEkNWcnRqSFydm7Mweuk=",
    "originContent": " 1. Build project with `Release` profile.",
    "translatedContent": " 1. `Release` 프로필로 프로젝트를 빌드하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "Zlz1J5Iki19fmbIR0R56eq0JtYBDQWaWGH1e2y27Yk8=",
    "originContent": " 2. Run `Scripts\\pack-zip.ps1`.",
    "translatedContent": " 2. `Scripts\\pack-zip.ps1`을 실행하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "F4XIEGWC0JlXu9t2uppBAKxy3dX1v3iAWpJwyxzza3I=",
    "originContent": " 3. You should find a file named `QuickLook.Plugin.WebViewPlus.qlplugin` in the project directory.",
    "translatedContent": " 3. 프로젝트 디렉터리에서 `QuickLook.Plugin.WebViewPlus.qlplugin` 파일을 찾을 수 있습니다."
  },
